Harrys My Free Farm Bash Bot (MFF Bash Bot) *** MOD Version ***
---------------------------------------------------------------

Additional functions:
- Transport from Farm 5 to Farm 1 also includes eggs

- Several bot functions are executed only if you reached the minimum appropriate player level. One example is the farmers market, which is accessible beginning with level 23.

- Option to claim daily 10 minute growth bonus on one field on a farm of your choice. The bot automatically selects the first field which has a remining growth time of more than 30 minutes.

Changes:
- Changed several game queries to prevent jq to crash under cygwin

Untested changes:

- Changes to megafield "check empty harvest device" function to possibly prevent multiple buying of harvest device.